transcripts.text: Your inheritance to revival is to start digging.  I say let the plows go deep.  Lord, we say it's being plowed up.  I believe more people will be saved in the next 20, 30 years than in the previous 2,000.  And it will cause the prodigals to run, to run back to you.  I have issued the call to millions in the secret place.  Come from your caves.  Come from your dens.  Come from your hiding places.  Report to your stations.  Report to the battle line.
